= Final Fantasy Mystic Quest - Armor =

This page documents all defensive equipment in Final Fantasy: Mystic Quest, including armor, shields, helmets, and accessories.

== Overview ==

FFMQ has a simplified equipment system with three defensive slots:
* '''Armor''' - Body protection
* '''Shield''' - Blocking capability
* '''Helmet''' - Head protection
* '''Accessory''' - Special effects

