== Defense Calculation ==

Physical damage reduction:
 Damage Reduction = (Armor_Def + Shield_Def + Helmet_Def) / 4

Magical damage reduction:
 Magic Reduction = (Armor_MDef + Shield_MDef + Helmet_MDef) / 6

